<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">编辑文件夹书签</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">您的书签会列出在文件管理器的左侧栏中。</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h2><span class="title">添加书签：</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开您想添加的文件夹(或位置)。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Click the window menu in the toolbar and pick <span class="gui">Bookmark this
      Location</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h2><span class="title">删除书签：</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps"><li class="steps"><p class="p">Right-click on the bookmark in the sidebar and select
      <span class="gui">Remove</span> from the menu.</p></li></ol></div>
</div></div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h2><span class="title">重命名书签：</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Right-click on the bookmark in the sidebar and select
      <span class="gui">Rename…</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">在<span class="gui">名称</span>文本框中，输入一个新的名称。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">重命名书签不会重命名对应的文件夹，如果您要添加两个不同位置，但是名称相同的文件夹，书签将会显示相同的名称，您将不能区分它们，在这种情况下，用书签名比文件名更容易查找。</p></div></div></div></div>
</li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
</div>
